      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Meticulously maintained and presented in showroom condition, it offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector. Every detail, from the pristine interior to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a standard of care that is increasingly rare. We invite you to inspect this exemplary specimen, which stands as a testament to engineering excellence and aesthetic perfection.",
