    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. You won't find another one this clean. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44900.0,
